  "notes": "Great-grandfather on the Sanderson line. Born in Duplin County, NC. Son of Isaac Sanderson (1831-1912) and Sylvia A. Kennedy (1830-1913). Father Isaac died August 5, 1912 in Duplin County, NC. Siblings: Leana (1868-), Martha Ann (1870-1952), Isaac Lebbaus (1874-1949), Mary Elizabeth (1877-1947). Also had older siblings Ivy (1848-), William A. (1859-1945), Orpah (1860-1940). Married Mary Elizabeth Smith. Four sons: Horry Lee (1901-1971), Norman P. (1904-), Albert Evans (1905-1946), John Jackson (1908-). Died 1913 in Georgia at age 47."
